result = []
column = []
for i in range(len(df)):
    target = df["행정구역"].str.split("(").str[0].str.split(" ").str[1:3][i]
    if target[1]:
        result.append(i)
        column.append(" ".join(target))
        print(" ".join(target))

def tops(df, target):
    top = 0
    index = 0
    for i in range(len(df)):
        check = df[target][i]
        if top < check:
            top = check
            index = i
        
    return index#i
